setUnitPosWeak 
Game: Armed Assault (1.04) 
Description: Set unit position rules. Mode may be one of:  "DOWN" - person goes 
 prone and stays prone. "UP" - person stands and stays standing. "Middle 
" - Kneel Position. ArmA version 1.04 "AUTO" - person chooses mode 
 according to circumstances. 
 
 
Syntax:  
 unitName setUnitPosWeak mode 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object 
mode: String As above 
Return Value: 
 Nothing